# Input

```html
<input #name>

@let greeting     =  'Hello '     +   name.value;

@let user = user$ | async;

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1,5 +1,2 @@
 <input #name />
-
-@let greeting = "Hello " + name.value;
-
-@let user = user$ | async;
+@let greeting = 'Hello ' + name.value; @let user = user$ | async;
```

# Output

```html
<input #name />
@let greeting = 'Hello ' + name.value; @let user = user$ | async;
```
